It's delicious.

285
00:11:52,912 --> 00:11:53,813
BEST MALA IN A WHILE

286
00:11:54,266 --> 00:11:56,549
This soupless tantanmen is amazing.

287
00:11:56,783 --> 00:11:58,651
It's so spicy!

288
00:11:59,819 --> 00:12:02,722
Is it spicier than
