327
00:13:43,623 --> 00:13:46,492
It's like the Korean jellyfish cold dish.

328
00:13:46,559 --> 00:13:49,762
The tanginess of bansans goes well
with the spiciness of tantanmen.

329
00:13:49,996 --> 00:13:51,898
They make a great pair.

